  "description": "Factors is a triple 4-quadrant modulator module for your EuroRack video synthesizer. Factors is a symmetrical contrast adjuster. The contrast adjustment is centered on the mid-gray value of 0.5 volts: a \"fade to gray\". The ability to simultaneously set the black point and white point with a single voltage controllable parameter opens up interesting visual possibilities. Learn more about Factors on our documentation website!"
